            elit, ut convallis ante magna eget nunc. Sed urna velit, finibus vel
            velit nec, dapibus hendrerit leo.
          </p>

          <p slot="attribution">
            Joseph Smithson, Class of 2025
          </p>

          <p slot="attribution-sub-text">
            Optional Eyebrow
          </p>

          <div slot="actions">
            <umd-element-call-to-action type="secondary">
              <a href="/" aria-label="link to homepage">Home Link</a>
            </umd-element-call-to-action>
            <umd-element-call-to-action type="secondary">
              <a href="/components" aria-label="link to components">
                Components Link
